  <entry>
    <title>Matlab在高数线代学习中的应用(一)</title>
    <link href="/Matlab%E5%9C%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%95%B0%E7%BA%BF%E4%BB%A3%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/"/>
    <url>/Matlab%E5%9C%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%95%B0%E7%BA%BF%E4%BB%A3%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Matlab是一个功能十分强大的数学软件，如果在高数和线代学习中可以熟练使用Matlab解决一些繁杂的计算问题，验证手工计算的正确性，对学习大有裨益。但是网络上的大多数博文都只是对某个问题提出解决方案，并没有一个完整的总结，给搜索带来了不便，因此，本系列博文将对高等数学和线性代数中Matlab的应用做一总结，方便读者查阅。因本人水平所限，博文中存在一些不当之处，欢迎各位读者在评论区提出批评和指正。</p><h3 id="高数"><a href="#高数" class="headerlink" title="高数"></a>高数</h3><h4 id="极限"><a href="#极限" class="headerlink" title="极限"></a>极限</h4><ol><li><p>计算$\displaystyle\lim_{x \rightarrow + \infty}(1+\frac{1}{x})^x$</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms xlimit((<span class="hljs-number">1</span>+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>/x)^x,x,<span class="hljs-built_in">inf</span>)   <span class="hljs-comment">%第一个参数为函数表达式，第二个参数为自变量，第三个参数为自变量趋向的值</span><span class="hljs-comment">%结果</span><span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=<span class="hljs-built_in">exp</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)</code></pre></div></li></ol><ol><li><p>计算$\displaystyle\lim_{x \rightarrow 3^+}f(x)=\frac{x-3}{|x-3|}$的极限</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms xlimit((x<span class="hljs-number">-3</span>)/<span class="hljs-built_in">abs</span>(x<span class="hljs-number">-3</span>),x,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-string">'right'</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">%right指示右极限,left指示左极限</span><span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span></code></pre></div></li></ol><h4 id="微分"><a href="#微分" class="headerlink" title="微分"></a>微分</h4><ol><li><p>求$f(x)=arcsin(\frac{2x}{1+x^2})$的导数</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms x f(x)f(x)=<span class="hljs-built_in">asin</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*x/(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>+x^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>));<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=diff(f,x,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)pretty(<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>)<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>        <span class="hljs-number">4</span> x------ - ---------<span class="hljs-number">2</span>         <span class="hljs-number">2</span>     <span class="hljs-number">2</span>x  + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>   (x  + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)---------------------    /           <span class="hljs-number">2</span>   \    |        <span class="hljs-number">4</span> x    |<span class="hljs-built_in">sqrt</span>| <span class="hljs-number">1</span> - --------- |    |       <span class="hljs-number">2</span>     <span class="hljs-number">2</span> |    \     (x  + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)  /<span class="hljs-comment">%可以用pretty()函数对结果进行美化</span></code></pre></div></li><li><p>求$f(x)=e^x+1$的反函数</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms x f(x)f=<span class="hljs-built_in">exp</span>(x)+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;finverse(f,x)<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span> = <span class="hljs-built_in">log</span>(x<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>)</code></pre></div></li><li><p>求$\frac{\partial^2 u}{\partial x \partial y},u=f(x,y)=xsin(xy)$</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms x ydiff(x*<span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(x*y), x, y)<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*x*<span class="hljs-built_in">cos</span>(x*y) - x^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*y*<span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(x*y)</code></pre></div></li><li><p>设$siny+e^x-xy^2=0$,求$\frac{\mathrm{d} y }{\mathrm{d} x}$</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms x y ff=<span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(y)+<span class="hljs-built_in">exp</span>(x)-x*y^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=-diff(f,x)/diff(f,y);pretty(<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>)<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=    <span class="hljs-number">2</span>- y  + <span class="hljs-built_in">exp</span>(x)- --------------<span class="hljs-built_in">cos</span>(y) - <span class="hljs-number">2</span> x y</code></pre></div></li><li><p>求$f(x)=ln(x)$按$(x-1)$的幂展开的6阶泰勒公式</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms x f(x)f=<span class="hljs-built_in">log</span>(x);<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=taylor(f,x,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-string">'order'</span>,<span class="hljs-number">7</span>); <span class="hljs-comment">%忽略7阶及以上小量</span>pretty(<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>)<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=        <span class="hljs-number">2</span>          <span class="hljs-number">3</span>          <span class="hljs-number">4</span>          <span class="hljs-number">5</span>          <span class="hljs-number">6</span>    (x - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)    (x - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)    (x - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)    (x - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)    (x - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)x - -------- + -------- - -------- + -------- - -------- - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>        <span class="hljs-number">2</span>          <span class="hljs-number">3</span>          <span class="hljs-number">4</span>          <span class="hljs-number">5</span>          <span class="hljs-number">6</span></code></pre></div></li></ol><h4 id="积分"><a href="#积分" class="headerlink" title="积分"></a>积分</h4><ul><li>一元积分</li></ul><ol><li><p>求$f(x)=\int{xcos^2x}dx$</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms x ff=x*(<span class="hljs-built_in">cos</span>(x))^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=int(f,x);pretty(<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>)<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=                <span class="hljs-number">2</span>    <span class="hljs-number">2</span>x <span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span> x)   <span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(x)    x---------- - ------- + --    <span class="hljs-number">4</span>          <span class="hljs-number">4</span>       <span class="hljs-number">4</span></code></pre></div></li><li><p>计算$\int_{0}^{\frac{\pi}{2}}{\frac{x+sinx}{1+cosx}}dx$</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms x ff=(x+<span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(x))/(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>+<span class="hljs-built_in">cos</span>(x));<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=int(f,x,<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">pi</span>/<span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=<span class="hljs-built_in">pi</span>/<span class="hljs-number">2</span></code></pre></div></li></ol><ul><li>多元积分</li></ul><ol><li>计算$\int_{0}^{1}\int_{x^2}^x\frac{1}{x^2+y^2}dxdy$</li></ol><div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">fun=@(x,y)<span class="hljs-number">1.</span>/<span class="hljs-built_in">sqrt</span>(x.^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>+y.^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)ymax=@(x)xymin=@(x)x^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>integral2(fun,<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,ymin,ymax)<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=<span class="hljs-number">0.4142</span></code></pre></div><ol><li>计算$\int_{0}^{\pi}\int_0^1\int_{-1}^{1}(ysinx+zcosx)dxdydz$</li></ol><div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">fun=@(x,y,z)y.*<span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(x)+z.*<span class="hljs-built_in">cos</span>(x)integral3(fun,<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">pi</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=<span class="hljs-number">2.0000</span></code></pre></div><h4 id="微分方程"><a href="#微分方程" class="headerlink" title="微分方程"></a>微分方程</h4><p>Dy代表y的导数，D2y代表y的二阶导数， D3y代表y的三阶导数…</p><ol><li><p>求解微分方程$\frac{\mathrm d y}{\mathrm d x}=10^{x+y}$</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">y=dsolve(<span class="hljs-string">'Dy-10^(x+y)=0'</span>,<span class="hljs-string">'x'</span>);pretty(y)y=            x<span class="hljs-built_in">log</span>(C1 - <span class="hljs-number">10</span> )- -------------    <span class="hljs-built_in">log</span>(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>)</code></pre></div></li><li><p>求微分方程$(1+x^2)y^{\prime\prime}=2xy^{\prime}$满足初值条件$y|_{x=0}=1,y^{\prime}|_{x=0}=1$的特解</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">y=dsolve(<span class="hljs-string">'(1+x^2)*D2y-2*x*Dy=0'</span>,<span class="hljs-string">'y(0)=1,Dy(0)=3'</span>,<span class="hljs-string">'x'</span>);pretty(y)y=    <span class="hljs-number">2</span>x (x  + <span class="hljs-number">3</span>) + <span class="hljs-number">1</span></code></pre></div></li></ol><h4 id="画函数图像"><a href="#画函数图像" class="headerlink" title="画函数图像"></a>画函数图像</h4><ol><li>画箕(ji)舌线$y=\frac{8}{x^2+4}$的函数图像 <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">x=<span class="hljs-built_in">linspace</span>(<span class="hljs-number">-6</span>,<span class="hljs-number">6</span>,<span class="hljs-number">100</span>);y=<span class="hljs-number">8.</span>/(x.^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>+<span class="hljs-number">4</span>);<span class="hljs-built_in">plot</span>(x,y)</code></pre></div></li></ol><img src="/2020/07/19/Matlab%E5%9C%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%95%B0%E7%BA%BF%E4%BB%A3%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/jishecurve.webp" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class="" title="This is an example image"><ol><li><p>画出$x^2+y^2+2x=2\sqrt{x^2+y^2}$的函数图像</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">fimplicit(@(x,y) x.^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>+y.^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>+<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*x<span class="hljs-number">-2</span>*(x.^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>+y.^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)^<span class="hljs-number">0.5</span>)</code></pre></div></li></ol>{% asset_img xin.webp This is an example image %}<ol><li><p>画出$\rho=2sin2\theta$的图像</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">theta = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0.01</span>:<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*<span class="hljs-built_in">pi</span>;rho=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*<span class="hljs-built_in">sin</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*theta);polar(theta,rho)</code></pre></div></li></ol><img src="/2020/07/19/Matlab%E5%9C%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%95%B0%E7%BA%BF%E4%BB%A3%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/four.webp" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class="" title="This is an example image"><ol><li><p>画出双曲抛物面$\frac{x^2}{2^2}-y^2=z$的图像</p> <div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">f = @(x,y,z) x.^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>/<span class="hljs-number">4</span> - y.^<span class="hljs-number">2</span> - z;fimplicit3(f,<span class="hljs-string">'EdgeColor'</span>,<span class="hljs-string">'none'</span>,<span class="hljs-string">'FaceAlpha'</span>,<span class="hljs-number">.5</span>)</code></pre></div></li></ol><img src="/2020/07/19/Matlab%E5%9C%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%95%B0%E7%BA%BF%E4%BB%A3%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/ma.webp" srcset="/img/loading.gif" class="" title="This is an example image"><h4 id="级数"><a href="#级数" class="headerlink" title="级数"></a>级数</h4><ol><li><p>讨论下列级数的敛散性</p><ol><li><p>$\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\limits\frac{1}{n^2}$</p><div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms nsymsum(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>/n^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">inf</span>)<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=<span class="hljs-built_in">pi</span>^<span class="hljs-number">2</span>/<span class="hljs-number">6</span></code></pre></div><p>2.$\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\limits(-1)^n$</p><div class="hljs"><pre><code class="hljs matlab">syms nsymsum((<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>)^n,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">inf</span>)<span class="hljs-built_in">ans</span>=NaN</code></pre></div></li></ol></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
    
